**Steps:**
- Materialize collection_permissions boundary handlers on AP runtime surfaces.
- Apply mock auth context extraction and tenant scoping at boundary ingress.
- Preserve policy hooks for permission evaluation and enforcement.
- Keep boundary contracts aligned to declared resource operations only.
- Expose stable boundary interfaces for service facade integration.

**Definition of Done:**
- AP boundary exists for collection_permissions with tenant-scoped mock-auth handling.
