- Semantic Acceptance (CAF-TCTX-01/Q-CPAP-TCTX-CONFLICT-01/claim_over_header/tenant_context_conflict_precedence_realization): Conflict handling remains explicit and coherent across CPâ†”AP contracts, boundary logic, and runtime composition.
