- TBP Gate (TBP-AUTH-MOCK-01/G-AUTH-MOCK-CONTRACT-REALIZATION): UI/UX claim builders must emit the same canonical bearer token shape resolved by the role-bound shared auth helper (current canonical shape: `mock.<base64-json>.token`) rather than a lane-local raw base64 variant.
- TBP Gate (TBP-AUTH-MOCK-01/G-AUTH-MOCK-CONTRACT-REALIZATION): UI claim construction and UI API header emission live in their actual owning surfaces rather than relying on a single proxy file to carry all evidence.
